<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: right;"><div style=""><div style="text-align: left;"><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" style="">Dear Parents,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">In recent days we have observed an increase in absence due to illness across the Campus. For the most part, these appear to be mild cases of cold or flu, but we have also received several reports of stomach illness. In two cases, these have been confirmed as the common <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/norovirus/">norovirus</a>.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Our priority on Lower Campus is to do everything possible to keep children in good health. Teachers will ensure children adhere to our hygiene procedures, and we will disinfect rooms across the Campus. We will also monitor students closely, and will request that children be taken home if concerning symptoms are apparent.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">We ask that parents cooperate with us by:</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">●&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Keeping children absent when they show clear signs of illness, (such as fever, vomiting or diarrhea).</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">●&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Informing classroom teachers promptly in cases of absence due to illness, with a description of the symptoms or illness.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">●&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Have children collected as promptly as is possible, when requested by the school.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">In case you have concerns about your child’s health, we recommend you see a doctor for professional advice.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Warm regards,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Justin Noack</font></div><div style=""><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" style=""><div style="">Head of Lower Campus</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Sent Via Admissions Office</div></font></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
